\domingofranco: Rizal, what is the purpose of this organization?
Rizal: La Liga Filipina will unite Filipinos and promote education and reform.
Reformist: Will this not anger the authorities?
Rizal: Change always invites opposition.
\domingofranco: What do you hope to achieve?
Rizal: A peaceful and just society where Filipinos have equal rights.
Reformist: Then we stand with you.
Rizal: Together, we can build a better future for our country.